  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n[comment]: # (A problem description)\r\nUser see how cursor jumps when we try to devide multiline line message into several messages\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNo jumps of a cursor\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nCursor jumps to the end of the message when there is a line break in the middle of the composer\r\nNo jumps of a cursor\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open chat\r\n2. Type multiline message\r\n3. Put a cursor at the end of one message string at the half of a multiline message\r\n4. Tap enter on the keyboard once and then twice \r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/147824399/52991a95-4779-4afc-8fd6-b1a65ca6ddb5\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly from the 17 of January\r\n- Operating System:  iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
